goal_text = "\"Well, you see, I recently had to, err, let go of my secretary, and I haven't been able to get hold of a new one yet.\" The fat man in the couch opposite you doesn't as much sit as he wallows, somehow managing to seep into every single fold of the imitation leather, like a massive blob of slime. \"That got me thinking, the tech is getting pretty good these days, and how hard could it really be to replace a secretary with AI? Right?\"

\"Well, Mr. Rutherford, it depends what you want this 'Secretary' of yours to be able to do,\" you reply.

\"Let's start simple. I need her to manage my schedule and reply to my emails.\"

\"Should be doable.\"
"
